<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>회원가입 · 뷰로그</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
  <div class="w-full max-w-sm">
    <div class="text-center mb-6">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">📽️</span>
        <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800">뷰로그</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">계정을 만들고 기록을 시작하세요</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6">
      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="mb-4 rounded-lg bg-red-50 border border-red-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-red-700"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/register" class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label class="label" for="username">아이디</label>
          <input class="field" type="text" id="username" name="username" value="<%= username %>" required autofocus placeholder="3자 이상">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="label" for="password">비밀번호</label>
          <input class="field" type="password" id="password" name="password" required placeholder="6자 이상">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="label" for="confirm">비밀번호 확인</label>
          <input class="field" type="password" id="confirm" name="confirm" required placeholder="비밀번호 재입력">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full">회원가입</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 mt-4">
      이미 계정이 있으신가요?
      <a href="/login" class="text-brand-600 font-medium hover:underline">로그인</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
